    cheatSheetLine: "Feed: hybrid fan-out. Real-time: WebSocket+push. Proximity: Geohash/Quadtree (9-cell search). Hot key: L1 cache + key split. High write: Kafka/Cassandra. Distributed tx: Saga.",
